I11(d) T4Electronic Publication of Notice of Solicitation, Award, or OrderK._A notice of solicitation, award, or order required to be published under subsection (a) shall be published by electronic means. The notice must be electronically accessible in a form that allows convenient and universal user access through the single Government-wide point of entry designated in the Federal Acquisition Regulation.

I11(e) T4Time Limitations._

