I12(2) T4Actions of administratorK._On receipt of a petition for adjustment of a dollar threshold under paragraph (1), the Administrator_

I13(A) shall determine, in writing, whether the dollar threshold is required to be adjusted under this section; and

I13(B) on determining that it should be adjusted, shall publish in the Federal Register a revised notice of the adjustment dollar thresholds under this section that includes the adjustment of the dollar threshold covered by the petition.

Q04

I12(3) T4Effective date of adjustment by petitionK._The adjustment of a dollar threshold pursuant to a petition under this subsection takes effect on the date the revised notice adding the adjustment under paragraph (2)(B) is published.

