I89. Actions required of procurement officers when contacted regarding non-Federal employment

I11(a) T4Actions RequiredK._An agency official participating personally and substantially in a Federal agency procurement for a contract in excess of the simplified acquisition threshold who contacts or is contacted by a person that is a bidder or offeror in that Federal agency procurement regarding possible non-Federal employment for that official shall_

