I89. Quantities to order

I11(a) T4Factors Affecting Quantity To OrderK._Each executive agency shall procure supplies in a quantity that_

I12(1) will result in the total cost and unit cost most advantageous to the Federal Government, where practicable; and

I12(2) does not exceed the quantity reasonably expected to be required by the agency.

